data.description: Welcome home! This 4-bed, 2-bath gem offers a generous 2,530 sqft of living space on 2.5 acres of land, adjacent to hundreds of acres of public-use (BLM) land. Not only is it a spacious retreat, but it also comes with an enticing $5,000 seller credit, unlocking various possibilities, including the potential to reduce your interest rate. The property includes a fully insulated shop/2-car garage with 100 amps dedicated to the shop, ensuring ample power for all your workshop needs. Book your showing today! Enjoy breathtaking year-round views from the covered deck in the backyard and the uncovered deck in the front, providing stunning perspectives of both sunrise and sunset over the mountains and desert.   The well-designed open floor plan includes a master bedroom with a walk-in closet, double sinks, a spacious shower, and a luxurious garden tub.  Inside, the home is adorned with stylish and practical touches, including luxury vinyl plank flooring in main areas, cozy carpeted bedrooms, and durable sheet vinyl in bathrooms. The laundry room already has plumbing for a sink, which has been capped off. You have the option to easily add a sink if desired.   This home not only offers comfort and functionality but also provides a unique opportunity to own a property with outdoor allure and a generous seller credit. Don't miss out on making this remarkable residence your very own!
